msgid "0:教室を出て、脇目も振らず昇降口へ向かう。[%p]"
msgstr "0:I left the classroom and raced to the front entrance of the school.[%p]"

msgid "100:ただしあくまで目立たないように、うなだれながら、廊下の端を歩くっていういつもの習慣は忘れない。[%p]"
msgstr "100:But of course, I didn't forget to walk along the side of the hallways with my head down.[%p]"

msgid "200:終業ベルが鳴ってから少し時間が経っているから、掃除当番やこれから部活の生徒たちは残っているけど、帰宅部はもうほとんどいない。[%p]"
msgstr "200:The bell had rung a little while ago, so the only kids left around were the ones on cleaning duty, or in clubs and on sports teams.[%p]"

msgid "300:放課後の学校って、どこか寂しげでノスタルジーを感じさせる。[linebreak]翠明学園みたいに新しい校舎だろうと、木造などの古い校舎だろうと、それは変わらない。[%p]"
msgstr "300:There was something slightly lonely and nostalgic about a school after the last bell rang. It didn't matter if it was an old wooden school, or a newer one like Suimei Academy.[%p]"

msgid "400:まあ、木造校舎についてはエロゲー内で行ったことがあるだけなんですけどね。[%p]"
msgstr "400:Not that I'd ever been to an old wooden school outside of an H-Game.[%p]"

msgid "500:そんな下らないことを考えながら、斜陽が射し込む廊下を歩いていたら、前方から奇妙な人影がやって来るのが見えた。[%p]"
msgstr "500:As I lost myself in thoughts of H-games with wooden school buildings, I could see a strange silhouette at the end of the hallway.[%p]"

msgid "600:女子が、大きなダンボールをふたつ抱えて、よたよたと歩いている。[%p]"
msgstr "600:It was a girl, slowly walking with two big cardboard boxes in her hands.[%p]"

msgid "700:そのダンボールに隠れて顔は見えない。[linebreak]たぶん彼女も前が見えていないだろう。[%p]"
msgstr "700:They were so big I couldn't see her face. She probably couldn't see in front of her, either.[%p]"

msgid "800:危なっかしいことこの上ない。[%p]"
msgstr "800:It was incredibly dangerous.[%p]"

msgid "900:こういう場合、エロゲーなら僕とあの女子が激突して、フラグ発生するのがお約束だ。[%p]"
msgstr "900:In an H-game, this would be my cue to run into her and start her route.[%p]"

msgid "1000:試してみようかと思ったけど、あくまで思っただけで、実際には行動に移す気もない。[%p]"
msgstr "1000:I thought about doing it, but I didn't actually try.[%p]"

msgid "1100:むしろ強く警戒した。[linebreak]こいつが『将軍』の刺客である可能性はじゅうぶんにある。[%p]"
msgstr "1100:If anything, I was really cautious around her. There was a decent chance she was one of Shogun's assassins.[%p]"

msgid "1200:関わるな。[linebreak]気をつけろ。[%p]"
msgstr "1200:I had to stay away from her. I had to be careful.[%p]"

msgid "1300:僕は慎重に彼女の足取りに注意を払う。[%p]"
msgstr "1300:I watched her feet closely.[%p]"

msgid "1400:女子は右へフラフラ、左へフラフラとしながらなおも近づいてくる。[%p]"
msgstr "1400:She was getting closer, staggering to the right, and then staggering to the left.[%p]"

msgid "1500:一方の僕は、廊下の左端を歩いていた。[%p]"
msgstr "1500:I was walking on the left side of the hallway.[%p]"

msgid "1600:女子が右側へ寄ったのを見計らって、歩くスピードを速める。[linebreak]そのままうまくすれ違った。[%p]"
msgstr "1600:When she headed toward the right, I picked up my pace. I managed to get past her without problems.[%p]"

msgid "1700:と、なにかが落ちる音がして、何気なく視線を下へ向けてみると――[%p]"
msgstr "1700:But then, when I heard something fall and looked down...[%p]"

msgid "1800:生徒手帳が落ちていた。[linebreak]つい、足を止めてしまう。[%p]"
msgstr "1800:I saw a student notebook. I stopped.[%p]"

msgid "1900:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "1900:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "2000:今のダンボール女子が、落としたのか？[%p]"
msgstr "2000:Had the cardboard box girl dropped it?[%p]"

msgid "2100:僕はその生徒手帳を凝視したまま、考えを巡らせる。[%p]"
msgstr "2100:I stared at it, trying to think.[%p]"

msgid "2200:脳裏に浮かんだのは、疑念。[%p]"
msgstr "2200:My first instinct was to be suspicious.[%p]"

msgid "2300:なんで、このタイミングで生徒手帳が落ちたのか。[%p]"
msgstr "2300:Why had she dropped her notebook just now?[%p]"

msgid "2400:あからさますぎる。まるで僕に拾わせようとしているみたいだ。[%p]"
msgstr "2400:The timing was too obvious. It was like she was trying to make me pick it up.[%p]"

msgid "2500:罠……？[%p]"
msgstr "2500:Could it be a trap?[%p]"

msgid "2600:わざと、落としたんだろうか。[%p]"
msgstr "2600:Had she dropped it deliberately?[%p]"

msgid "2700:ダンボール女子は両手でダンボールを抱えていた。[%p]"
msgstr "2700:She was holding the boxes with both hands.[%p]"

msgid "2800:手は塞がっていた。[%p]"
msgstr "2800:She didn't have a hand free to do anything.[%p]"

msgid "2900:もし生徒手帳がスカートのポケットに入っていたなら、それを“取り出してわざと落とす”っていう行動は不可能だ。[%p]"
msgstr "2900:If her notebook had been in her skirt pocket, it would be impossible for her to take it out and drop it on the floor deliberately.[%p]"

msgid "3000:ただ、僕は、そもそもこの生徒手帳がどこから落ちたのか見たわけじゃない。[%p]"
msgstr "3000:But... I hadn't seen where it had come from.[%p]"

msgid "3100:もしかするとダンボール女子は、最初からダンボールで[linebreak]隠すようにして手に持っていたかもしれないんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "3100:Maybe the cardboard box girl had it in her hand the whole time, and was using the boxes to hide it?[%p]"

msgid "3200:確信はない。[linebreak]わざとじゃないかもしれない。[linebreak]偶然って考える方が普通だろう。[%p]"
msgstr "3200:I couldn't be sure. Maybe it wasn't deliberate. Most people would assume it was just a coincidence.[%p]"

msgid "3300:それで僕は、ダンボール女子の姿を目で追った。[linebreak]追おうとした。[%p]"
msgstr "3300:I watched the cardboard box girl to see what she'd do. Or tried, rather.[%p]"

msgid "3400:[name]拓巳[line]「あ……」[%p]"
msgstr "3400:[name]拓巳[line]Oh...[%p]"

msgid "3500:まさにちょうどその瞬間、ダンボール女子は廊下を曲がっていってしまった。[%p]"
msgstr "3500:Just then, she'd rounded a corner.[%p]"

msgid "3600:後ろ姿が一瞬見えただけだった。[linebreak]たぶん、見覚えのない女子だ。[%p]"
msgstr "3600:I'd only seen her from behind for an instant. It wasn't anybody I knew... probably.[%p]"

msgid "3700:髪は……短かったような気がする。[%p]"
msgstr "3700:Her hair seemed short... Maybe.[%p]"

msgid "3800:いや、でも長かったようにも見えた。[%p]"
msgstr "3800:No, it also seemed long.[%p]"

msgid "3900:はっきりとどっちって言い切ることができない。[%p]"
msgstr "3900:I couldn't be sure.[%p]"

msgid "4000:顔も、当然ながら見ていない。[linebreak]すれ違ったときはダンボールに隠れていた。[%p]"
msgstr "4000:And of course, I hadn't seen her face. It'd been hidden by the boxes when we'd passed each other.[%p]"

msgid "4100:僕と生徒手帳は、廊下に取り残された。[%p]"
msgstr "4100:The hallway was empty, except for me and the student notebook.[%p]"

msgid "4200:拾って、職員室に届けるなり、さっきのダンボール女子を追いかけるなりするのが常識的な行動なのかもしれない。[linebreak]でも僕は、それをすることを躊躇した。[%p]"
msgstr "4200:The normal thing to do would be to pick it up and take it to the teacher's office, or run after the cardboard box girl and bring it to her. But I was hesitant to do that.[%p]"

msgid "4300:周囲を見回す。[linebreak]他に生徒は見当たらない。[%p]"
msgstr "4300:I looked around. There weren't any other students nearby.[%p]"

msgid "4400:遠くで、複数の女子が楽しそうな笑い声を上げているのが聞こえるぐらい。[%p]"
msgstr "4400:I could hear a group of girls laughing in the distance, but that was all.[%p]"

msgid "4500:これが罠とは思えない。[%p]"
msgstr "4500:It was hard to believe this could be a trap.[%p]"

msgid "4600:手帳の持ち主はすでにこの場にいない。[%p]"
msgstr "4600:The person who owned it was already gone.[%p]"

msgid "4700:この状況でどうやって僕を罠にはめようって言うんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "4700:What could they do to me?[%p]"

msgid "4800:手帳に超小型爆弾でも挟まってるとでも？[linebreak]それこそ非現実的すぎる。[%p]"
msgstr "4800:Was there a miniature bomb attached to it? No, that was ridiculous.[%p]"

msgid "4900:だからきっと、今ここで僕が手帳を拾ったとしても、別になにも起こらないんだろう。[%p]"
msgstr "4900:So, even if I picked up the notebook, nothing bad would happen to me.[%p]"

msgid "5000:そうだ。そうに決まってる。[%p]"
msgstr "5000:That's right. Yeah, that had to be right.[%p]"

msgid "5100:念のために、手帳であの女子が何者なのかを確認しておくべきだ。[linebreak]『将軍』の手下かもしれないから。[%p]"
msgstr "5100:Just in case, I should check who the girl was. She might be working with Shogun, after all.[%p]"

msgid "5200:名前とクラス、顔写真だけ確認して、手帳そのものはここに放置しておこう。[%p]"
msgstr "5200:I could check her class, her photo, and her name, and then put it right back on the ground.[%p]"

msgid "5300:わざわざ本人に届けに行くなんて面倒なことはごめんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "5300:I certainly wasn't going to waste my time going to find her.[%p]"

msgid "5400:僕はなおも慎重に周囲へ視線を巡らせて誰もいないことを確かめてから、生徒手帳を拾い、何気なく最初のページを開いた。[%p]"
msgstr "5400:After taking several glances around to make sure nobody was nearby, I picked it up and flipped to the first page.[%p]"

msgid "5500:[name]拓巳[line]「ひ……っ！」[%p]"
msgstr "5500:[name]拓巳[line]Aah...![%p]"

msgid "5600:慌てて手帳を放り捨てる。[%p]"
msgstr "5600:I quickly threw the notebook to the floor.[%p]"

msgid "5700:なんだよ、今の……。[linebreak]得体の知れない薄気味悪さ。[%p]"
msgstr "5700:What the hell was that? I had this awful, creepy feeling in the pit of my stomach.[%p]"

msgid "5800:怖いというより、気持ちが悪い。[%p]"
msgstr "5800:It wasn't scary as much as it was sickening.[%p]"

msgid "5900:悪質な、でも明確な、僕個人へ向けた嫌がらせ。[%p]"
msgstr "5900:Somebody had set this whole thing up to get at me.[%p]"

msgid "6000:誰だ……。[linebreak]誰がこんなことを……。[%p]"
msgstr "6000:Who? Who would do this?[%p]"

msgid "6100:って、さっきの女子に決まってるだろ！[%p]"
msgstr "6100:It had to be that girl![%p]"

msgid "6200:あの女、やっぱり『将軍』の手下だったんだ。そうに違いない……。[%p]"
msgstr "6200:She was working with Shogun after all! I knew it.[%p]"

msgid "6300:生徒手帳の中身は、チラリと見ただけだけど……。[%p]"
msgstr "6300:I'd only seen the inside of the notebook for a second, but...[%p]"

msgid "6400:最初のページにあるはずの、持ち主の名前や生年月日、クラスなどの情報はすべて黒く塗り潰されていた。[%p]"
msgstr "6400:Its owner's name, birthday, class... everything that was supposed to be on the first page was blacked out.[%p]"

msgid "6500:さらに本来貼ってあるはずの顔写真も、剥がされていた。[%p]"
msgstr "6500:The photo had been ripped out, too.[%p]"

msgid "6600:気持ち悪い……っ。[%p]"
msgstr "6600:I felt sick.[%p]"

msgid "6700:[name]拓巳[line]「……うっ」[%p]"
msgstr "6700:[name]拓巳[line]Ugh...[%p]"

msgid "6800:唐突に、吐き気をもよおした。[%p]"
msgstr "6800:I suddenly felt like throwing up.[%p]"

msgid "6900:この場から一刻も早く立ち去りたかった。[%p]"
msgstr "6900:I wanted to get out of here as soon as I could.[%p]"

msgid "7000:僕は口を押さえながら、階段へ向かった。[%p]"
msgstr "7000:I ran for the stairs, hands over my mouth.[%p]"

msgid "7100:無我夢中で中庭へ出たところで、嘔吐するのを我慢しきれなくなった。[%p]"
msgstr "7100:By the time I made it to the courtyard, I couldn't hold it in anymore.[%p]"

msgid "7200:その場にひざまずいた途端、胃の中のものが逆流してくる。[%p]"
msgstr "7200:The second I dropped to my knees, the contents of my stomach came flooding up my throat.[%p]"

msgid "7300:教室を出て、昇降口へ向かおうとした。[%p]"
msgstr "7300:I left the classroom and headed to the front entrance of the school.[%p]"

msgid "7400:でも途中で思いとどまり、回れ右して１年生の教室がある校舎の方へと向かう。[%p]"
msgstr "7400:But on the way there, I changed my mind and headed back to the building where the first-year students were.[%p]"

msgid "7500:いつも使っている昇降口は避けた方がいいかもって思ったんだ。[linebreak]『将軍』や優愛が待ち伏せしてる可能性も捨てきれない。[%p]"
msgstr "7500:It felt like I'd do better to avoid the main gate. There was a chance Shogun or Yua might be waiting for me there.[%p]"

msgid "7600:だから別ルートから学校を出ることにした。[%p]"
msgstr "7600:I decided to leave by another route.[%p]"

msgid "7700:１年生の校舎へは渡り廊下を使う。[%p]"
msgstr "7700:I used the connecting corridor that led to the first-year students' building.[%p]"

msgid "7800:終業ベルが鳴ってから少し時間が経っているから、掃除当番やこれから部活の生徒たちは残っているけど、帰宅部はもうほとんどいない。[%p]"
msgstr "7800:The bell had rung a little while ago, so the only kids left around were the ones on cleaning duty, or in clubs and on sports teams.[%p]"

msgid "7900:放課後の学校って、どこか寂しげでノスタルジーを感じさせる。[linebreak]翠明学園みたいに新しい校舎だろうと、木造などの古い校舎だろうと、それは変わらない。[%p]"
msgstr "7900:There was something slightly lonely and nostalgic about a school after the last bell rang. It didn't matter if it was an old wooden school, or a newer one like Suimei Academy.[%p]"

msgid "8000:まあ、木造校舎についてはエロゲー内で行ったことがあるだけなんですけどね。[%p]"
msgstr "8000:Not that I'd ever been to an old wooden school outside of an H-Game.[%p]"

msgid "8100:いずれにせよ、校内には静けさが漂っていた。[%p]"
msgstr "8100:Either way, the school was quiet.[%p]"

msgid "8200:僕はその静寂の中を、なるべく足音を立てないようにしつつ、足早に歩く。[%p]"
msgstr "8200:I walked as quickly and quietly as I could through the silence.[%p]"

msgid "8300:窓から射し込んでくる西日が、暖かい。[%p]"
msgstr "8300:The setting sun felt warm through the windows.[%p]"

msgid "8400:いつもはうなだれて歩いているけど、今はすれ違う生徒もいないから、むしろ前をしっかり見据えて、怪しい人影が潜んでいないかに注意を向ける。[%p]"
msgstr "8400:Normally, I walked with my head down. But there were no other students around me, so I walked with my head held up, alert, watching for anybody suspicious.[%p]"

msgid "8500:音――[%p]"
msgstr "8500:Sound...[%p]"

msgid "8600:音が、聞こえる。[%p]"
msgstr "8600:I could hear a sound.[%p]"

msgid "8700:この音はなんだろう……前にもどこかで聞いたことがあるような――[%p]"
msgstr "8700:What was it? It felt like I'd heard it somewhere before.[%p]"

msgid "8800:直後、前方に見える１年生校舎の廊下を、すっと横切るものがあった。[%p]"
msgstr "8800:Then I saw something pass across my vision and down the corridor at the end of the hallway.[%p]"

msgid "8900:誰も乗っていない、車椅子……。[%p]"
msgstr "8900:It was an empty wheelchair.[%p]"

msgid "9000:脳裏に、昨日見た『集団ダイブ』の映像が浮かぶ。[linebreak]背筋が凍りつき、僕はその場に立ち止まった。[%p]"
msgstr "9000:Images of the Group Dive I'd seen yesterday came into my mind. I felt a chill run down my spine, and froze.[%p]"

msgid "9100:廊下を横切った車椅子は、僕の視界から消え――[%p]"
msgstr "9100:The wheelchair vanished from my vision...[%p]"

msgid "9200:すぐに、ものすごい音が聞こえてきた。[%p]"
msgstr "9200:And then I heard an incredibly loud noise.[%p]"

msgid "9300:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "9300:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "9400:静寂が戻ってくる。[%p]"
msgstr "9400:The silence returned.[%p]"

msgid "9500:僕は息を詰め、音のした方をじっと見つめた。[%p]"
msgstr "9500:I held my breath and stared in the direction the sound seemed to have come from.[%p]"

msgid "9600:今のは……なんだ？[%p]"
msgstr "9600:What did I just see?[%p]"

msgid "9700:どうして、学校に車椅子が……？[linebreak]しかも、無人のまま動いていた。[%p]"
msgstr "9700:Why was there a wheelchair at school? And why wasn't anybody sitting in it?[%p]"

msgid "9800:最後の衝撃音は、車椅子が階段を転がり落ちていった音だろう。[linebreak]あれだけの音がしたっていうことは、無惨に大破してるはず。[%p]"
msgstr "9800:That last noise was probably the sound of the wheelchair falling down the stairs. If it was that loud, the chair was probably broken into pieces now.[%p]"

msgid "9900:とっさに周囲を見回す。[linebreak]静かなのが逆に恐怖をかき立てる。[%p]"
msgstr "9900:I looked around. The quiet suddenly seemed eerie.[%p]"

msgid "10000:少なくともこの場所からは、動くものは見つけられない。[%p]"
msgstr "10000:From where I was standing, at least, I couldn't see anything moving.[%p]"

msgid "10100:だけど――[%p]"
msgstr "10100:But...[%p]"

msgid "10200:視線を、[linebreak]感じる。[%p]"
msgstr "10200:I could feel... a gaze.[%p]"

msgid "10300:――僕を見るな。[%p]"
msgstr "10300:—Don't look at me.[%p]"

msgid "10400:まさか、『将軍』が、いるの……？[linebreak]この学校に、来てるの……？[%p]"
msgstr "10400:Was... Shogun here? Was he at the school?[%p]"

msgid "10500:なにをしに来たの？[linebreak]優愛に会うため？[linebreak]僕に、会うため？[%p]"
msgstr "10500:Why? To meet with Yua? To find me?[%p]"

msgid "10600:僕は一歩、後ずさった。[%p]"
msgstr "10600:I took a step back.[%p]"

msgid "10700:その拍子に転びそうになった。[linebreak]なんとかバランスを保つ。[%p]"
msgstr "10700:When I did, I almost fell backward. I somehow managed to retain my balance.[%p]"

msgid "10800:薄気味悪い。[%p]"
msgstr "10800:I felt cold and clammy.[%p]"

msgid "10900:嫌がらせのつもり？[%p]"
msgstr "10900:Was this some kind of prank?[%p]"

msgid "11000:なんで姿を現さないんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "11000:Why wouldn't they show themselves?[%p]"

msgid "11100:よっぽど、目の前に本人が現れてくれた方がマシだった。[%p]"
msgstr "11100:I'd feel better if they actually just showed up.[%p]"

msgid "11200:[name]拓巳[line]「……うっ」[%p]"
msgstr "11200:[name]拓巳[line]Ugh...[%p]"

msgid "11300:唐突に、吐き気をもよおした。[%p]"
msgstr "11300:I suddenly felt like throwing up.[%p]"

msgid "11400:この場から一刻も早く立ち去りたかった。[%p]"
msgstr "11400:I wanted to get out of here as soon as I could.[%p]"

msgid "11500:僕は口を押さえながら、来た道を引き返した。[%p]"
msgstr "11500:I ran back the way I'd come, holding my hands over my mouth.[%p]"

msgid "11600:階段を駆け下り、無我夢中で中庭へ出たところで、嘔吐するのを我慢しきれなくなった。[%p]"
msgstr "11600:By the time I made it down the stairs and into to the courtyard, I couldn't hold it in anymore.[%p]"

msgid "11700:その場にひざまずいた途端、胃の中のものが逆流してくる。[%p]"
msgstr "11700:The second I dropped to my knees, the contents of my stomach came flooding up my throat.[%p]"

msgid "11800:勢いよく立ち上がり、[linebreak]カバンを担いで教室から出ようと顔を上げたら――[%p]"
msgstr "11800:After that, I leaped up, bag in hand and ready to go.[%p]"

msgid "11900:ドアのところに、あの女がたたずんで、[%p]"
msgstr "11900:But that girl was standing at the door,[%p]"

msgid "12000:僕を見ていた。[%p]"
msgstr "12000:looking at me.[%p]"

msgid "12100:[name]拓巳[line]「わああああーーーっ！」[%p]"
msgstr "12100:[name]拓巳[line]W-Waaaaah![%p]"

msgid "12200:思わず悲鳴を上げてしまう。[%p]"
msgstr "12200:I screamed.[%p]"

msgid "12300:まだ教室には半分近いクラスメイトが残っていた。みんなの冷ややかな視線が、一斉に僕へと集まる。[%p]"
msgstr "12300:Half my classmates were still in the room. I could feel them staring at me coldly.[%p]"

msgid "12400:――やめろっ！[%p]"
msgstr "12400:—Stop![%p]"

msgid "12500:逃げろ……！[%p]"
msgstr "12500:Run away...[%p]"

msgid "12600:――僕を見るなっ！[%p]"
msgstr "12600:—Don't look at me![%p]"

msgid "12700:逃げろ……！[%p]"
msgstr "12700:Run away...[%p]"

msgid "12800:――僕を見ないでくれっ！[%p]"
msgstr "12800:—Please don't look at me![%p]"

msgid "12900:逃げるんだ……！[%p]"
msgstr "12900:RUN![%p]"

msgid "13000:パニックになりながらも、僕はクラスメイトたちを押しのけて、優愛がたたずんでいたのとは別のドアから教室を飛び出した。[%p]"
msgstr "13000:Panicking, I knocked aside my classmates and headed out the other door, the one opposite from where Yua was standing.[%p]"

msgid "13100:無我夢中で中庭まで逃げてきたところで、強烈な吐き気に襲われた。[%p]"
msgstr "13100:I ran until I made it to the courtyard, where I was suddenly overtaken by the urge to vomit.[%p]"

msgid "13200:我慢しようとしたけど無理だった。[%p]"
msgstr "13200:I tried to hold it in, but it was useless.[%p]"

msgid "13300:その場にひざまずき、嘔吐してしまう。[%p]"
msgstr "13300:I dropped to my knees and threw up.[%p]"

msgid "13400:[name]拓巳[line]「げほ……うえ……がは……」[%p]"
msgstr "13400:[name]拓巳[line]Gweeh... Wheh... Gwah...[%p]"

msgid "13500:のどの奥が、逆流してきた胃酸のせいでヒリヒリとする。[%p]"
msgstr "13500:Stomach acid stung my throat.[%p]"

msgid "13600:涙で視界がにじんでる。[%p]"
msgstr "13600:My eyes were blurry.[%p]"

msgid "13700:息が苦しい。[%p]"
msgstr "13700:It hurt to breathe.[%p]"

msgid "13800:口の中が吐瀉物の後味で気持ち悪い。[%p]"
msgstr "13800:There was a disgusting taste left in my mouth from the vomit.[%p]"

msgid "13900:自分で考えていた以上に、[linebreak]僕は精神的に追い詰められているみたいだ……。[%p]"
msgstr "13900:I guess I was under a lot more stress than I thought I was…[%p]"

msgid "14000:徹夜したせいもあるかも……。[%p]"
msgstr "14000:Maybe it was because I'd been up all night.[%p]"

msgid "14100:口の端を拭いながら、せわしなく周囲を見回した。誰の姿もない。[%p]"
msgstr "14100:I wiped the edges of my mouth as I looked around frantically. Nobody was there.[%p]"

msgid "14200:でも、普段はなにも気にならない物陰や死角が、今の僕には恐ろしくてしょうがなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "14200:But the blind spots and shadows that I normally ignored now seemed terrifying to me.[%p]"

msgid "14300:どこかに、優愛や『将軍』が潜んでいるんじゃないかって思えてくる。[%p]"
msgstr "14300:I started to think that Yua and Shogun could be lurking anywhere.[%p]"

msgid "14400:そう思い込んじゃったら、もう一歩もその場から動けなくなった。[%p]"
msgstr "14400:And once the idea was in my head, I couldn't take another step.[%p]"

msgid "14500:誰か、助けて……。[%p]"
msgstr "14500:Somebody... help me.[%p]"

msgid "14600:泣きたくなった。[linebreak]と同時にまたも吐き気がこみ上げてきた。[%p]"
msgstr "14600:I wanted to cry. And the urge to vomit came back, too.[%p]"

msgid "14700:今度は吐きはしなかったけど、何度も空えずきを繰り返す。[%p]"
msgstr "14700:This time I didn't throw up, but I coughed and gasped for air.[%p]"

msgid "14800:苦しくて、ますます涙が溢れ出す。[%p]"
msgstr "14800:It hurt so much that even more tears came.[%p]"

msgid "14900:と、背中を誰かの手がそっとさすってきた。[%p]"
msgstr "14900:Then I felt a soft hand rubbing my back.[%p]"

msgid "15000:怯えつつ振り返る。[%p]"
msgstr "15000:I turned around, afraid.[%p]"

msgid "15100:[name]梨深[line]「大丈夫」[%p]"
msgstr "15100:[name]梨深[line]It's okay.[%p]"

msgid "15200:梨深が、そこにいた。[%p]"
msgstr "15200:Rimi was there.[%p]"

msgid "15300:[name]梨深[line]「大丈夫だよ」[%p]"
msgstr "15300:[name]梨深[line]Everything's okay.[%p]"

msgid "15400:その言葉は僕への問いかけではなくて。[%p]"
msgstr "15400:She wasn't asking me.[%p]"

msgid "15500:優しい、断定。[%p]"
msgstr "15500:She was gently telling me.[%p]"

msgid "15600:[name]梨深[line]「あたしは、タクの味方だから」[%p]"
msgstr "15600:[name]梨深[line]I'm on your side.[%p]"

msgid "15700:僕が吐いた汚物のすえた匂いに顔をしかめることもなく。[%p]"
msgstr "15700:She showed no sign of disgust at the smell of my vomit,[%p]"

msgid "15800:涙と鼻水にまみれ、口の端には吐瀉物までこびりつかせた僕の顔を見ても蔑むような態度も見せず。[%p]"
msgstr "15800:or the way my face was covered in snot and tears, with dried remains of my stomach's contents crusting the corners of my mouth.[%p]"

msgid "15900:僕を安心させるかのように、穏やかな微笑みを浮かべて。[%p]"
msgstr "15900:She had a gentle smile on her face, as if she was trying to make me feel better.[%p]"

msgid "16000:僕のすぐそばに寄り添って。[linebreak]そっと背中をさすってくれている。[%p]"
msgstr "16000:She came up to me... And rubbed my back gently.[%p]"

msgid "16100:どうして――[%p]"
msgstr "16100:Why...[%p]"

msgid "16200:この前も、今も、[%p]"
msgstr "16200:When I'd wanted somebody to save me before,[%p]"

msgid "16300:助けてほしいって思ったときに、[%p]"
msgstr "16300:she'd appeared then, too,[%p]"

msgid "16400:梨深は、僕の前に颯爽と現れてくれるんだろう。[%p]"
msgstr "16400:like a superhero coming to save the day.[%p]"

msgid "16500:梨深が今、こうしてここにいてくれることで。[%p]"
msgstr "16500:Why was it that having her around made me feel so much safer?[%p]"

msgid "16600:安心する。[linebreak]気が楽になる。[%p]"
msgstr "16600:Why did I feel so much better?[%p]"

msgid "16700:気が付けば、僕は自分の想いを吐露していた。[%p]"
msgstr "16700:The next thing I knew, I was spilling my guts out to her...[%p]"

msgid "16800:自分のことを話すのは苦手なのに。[%p]"
msgstr "16800:Even though I hated talking about myself.[%p]"

msgid "16900:[name]拓巳[line]「助けて……」[%p]"
msgstr "16900:[name]拓巳[line]Help me...[%p]"

msgid "17000:[name]拓巳[line]「ひとりは……怖い……んだ……」[%p]"
msgstr "17000:[name]拓巳[line]I'm afraid... of being alone...[%p]"

msgid "17100:だから、学校に来たのかもしれない。[%p]"
msgstr "17100:Maybe that's why I'd come to school today.[%p]"

msgid "17200:今までは、ひとりの方がいいって思ってた。[%p]"
msgstr "17200:Until now, I'd always thought I was better off alone.[%p]"

msgid "17300:もちろん今でも、誰かと話したりすることは、怖い。[%p]"
msgstr "17300:Of course, I was still afraid of talking to anybody.[%p]"

msgid "17400:人と接することに僕は自信がない。[%p]"
msgstr "17400:I didn't think I had any hope of being friends with them.[%p]"

msgid "17500:でもそれ以上に、『将軍』や優愛に追い詰められて、ひとりでいることがすごく不安で、怖くて、寂しくて。[%p]"
msgstr "17500:But after everything I was going through with Yua and Shogun, I felt so scared and lonely.[%p]"

msgid "17600:誰かに、そばにいてほしかった。[%p]"
msgstr "17600:I wanted somebody to be by my side.[%p]"

msgid "17700:優しくなんてしてもらえなくてもいい。[linebreak]ただ、誰かのいる場所にいたかった。[%p]"
msgstr "17700:I didn't even need them to be nice to me. I just needed them to be there.[%p]"

msgid "17800:[name]拓巳[line]「ひとりは……怖い……」[%p]"
msgstr "17800:[name]拓巳[line]I'm afraid of being alone.[%p]"

msgid "17900:[name]梨深[line]「だったら」[%p]"
msgstr "17900:[name]梨深[line]Then...[%p]"

msgid "18000:[name]梨深[line]「あたしが、一緒にいてあげる」[%p]"
msgstr "18000:[name]梨深[line]I'll be there for you.[%p]"

msgid "18100:その言葉には、[linebreak]なんの邪気もなく。[linebreak]なんの躊躇もなく。[%p]"
msgstr "18100:In her words, there was no malice, no hesitation.[%p]"

msgid "18200:[name]梨深[line]「さすがに、２４時間ずっとは無理だけど。たはは」[%p]"
msgstr "18200:[name]梨深[line]Of course, I can't be there for you 24 hours a day! Tahaha.[%p]"

msgid "18300:はにかんだ彼女の視線がふと空を見上げた。[%p]"
msgstr "18300:She smiled, and suddenly looked up at the sky.[%p]"

msgid "18400:遠い目をして、いったいなにを見ているんだろう。[%p]"
msgstr "18400:What was she looking at? It felt like she was staring at something far off in the distance.[%p]"

msgid "18500:[name]梨深[line]「朝、一緒に学校行って」[%p]"
msgstr "18500:[name]梨深[line]I'll go to school with you.[%p]"

msgid "18600:[name]梨深[line]「学校では休み時間にどうでもいいこと話して」[%p]"
msgstr "18600:[name]梨深[line]On break, we can talk about whatever.[%p]"

msgid "18700:[name]梨深[line]「お昼休みは、一緒にご飯食べて」[%p]"
msgstr "18700:[name]梨深[line]At lunch, we can eat together.[%p]"

msgid "18800:[name]梨深[line]「夕方、一緒に帰って」[%p]"
msgstr "18800:[name]梨深[line]And then, in the evening, we can go home together.[%p]"

msgid "18900:[name]梨深[line]「帰るついでにたまにどこかのお店に寄ったりして」[%p]"
msgstr "18900:[name]梨深[line]Sometimes, we might stop somewhere on the way.[%p]"

msgid "19000:[name]梨深[line]「タクの部屋で、ちょっとだけお喋りして」[%p]"
msgstr "19000:[name]梨深[line]Or maybe have a little chat in your room.[%p]"

msgid "19100:[name]梨深[line]「それで、また明日ねって、手を振って別れて」[%p]"
msgstr "19100:[name]梨深[line]And then I'll wave goodbye and say I'll see you tomorrow.[%p]"

msgid "19200:[name]梨深[line]「そんなのでいいなら、あたし、いくらでもしてあげるよ」[%p]"
msgstr "19200:[name]梨深[line]If that's all you need, I can give it to you.[%p]"

msgid "19300:[name]梨深[line]「……そういうの、結構、憧れなんだ」[%p]"
msgstr "19300:[name]梨深[line]I always wanted to do something like that.[%p]"

msgid "19400:それって……まるで……[%p]"
msgstr "19400:But that almost...[%p]"

msgid "19500:まるで、恋人みたいじゃないか……。[%p]"
msgstr "19500:Almost sounds like you'd be my girlfriend.[%p]"

msgid "19600:僕はあ然としてしまった。[%p]"
msgstr "19600:I was in shock.[%p]"

msgid "19700:これって本気で言ってる……よなあ、梨深の顔を見る限り。[%p]"
msgstr "19700:She was serious, at least, as near as I could tell from looking at her.[%p]"

msgid "19800:[name]拓巳[line]「ど、どうして……」[%p]"
msgstr "19800:[name]拓巳[line]W-Why?[%p]"

msgid "19900:[name]梨深[line]「ん？」[%p]"
msgstr "19900:[name]梨深[line]Hmm?[%p]"

msgid "20000:[name]拓巳[line]「どう、して……そこまで、してくれ……るの？」[%p]"
msgstr "20000:[name]拓巳[line]W-Why are you willing to do all this?[%p]"

msgid "20100:[name]梨深[line]「それは……」[%p]"
msgstr "20100:[name]梨深[line]Because...[%p]"

msgid "20200:それは……？[%p]"
msgstr "20200:Because?[%p]"

msgid "20300:これって明らかにフラグ立ってるよね？[%p]"
msgstr "20300:This was leading where I thought it was, right?[%p]"

msgid "20400:“タクのことが好きだから”とか言われてもおかしくないシチュエーションだよね？[%p]"
msgstr "20400:Her next words might be, “Because I like you, right?”[%p]"

msgid "20500:梨深が僕を好きになる理由はさっぱり分からないけど。[%p]"
msgstr "20500:I couldn't understand what about me she could possibly like, though.[%p]"

msgid "20600:いや、待て。これは孔明の罠だ。[%p]"
msgstr "20600:No, wait. This was a “Koumei's Trap.” A clever trick to get me to let my guard down.[%p]"

msgid "20700:前にも似たようなことがあった……。[%p]"
msgstr "20700:It'd happened before, right?[%p]"

msgid "20800:優愛のときはまんまと騙されて、絶望の淵に突き落とされた。[%p]"
msgstr "20800:Yua had deceived me, and then betrayed me.[%p]"

msgid "20900:だから過剰な期待はしちゃダメだ。[%p]"
msgstr "20900:I couldn't get my hopes up.[%p]"

msgid "21000:最悪の場合を想定しろ。[%p]"
msgstr "21000:I needed to imagine the worst-case scenario.[%p]"

msgid "21100:梨深も、やっぱり僕の敵かもしれ――[%p]"
msgstr "21100:Rimi might be my enemy, too.[%p]"

msgid "21200:[name]梨深[line]「ビシィッ！」[%p]"
msgstr "21200:[name]梨深[line]Snap![%p]"

msgid "21300:[name]拓巳[line]「っ！？」[%p]"
msgstr "21300:[name]拓巳[line]?![%p]"

msgid "21400:いきなり敬礼された。[%p]"
msgstr "21400:She suddenly saluted me.[%p]"

msgid "21500:唐突な行動に僕は動揺し、ついに梨深も本性を現すのかもしれないって愕然となりかけたけど。[%p]"
msgstr "21500:I was caught off-guard by her sudden action, and worried that she might suddenly be about to reveal her horrible true nature.[%p]"

msgid "21600:梨深の顔には、あくまで柔らかい笑みが浮かんだままだった。[%p]"
msgstr "21600:But I could still see the gentle smile on her face.[%p]"

msgid "21700:[name]梨深[line]「そんなの、友達だからに決まってるでしょ」[%p]"
msgstr "21700:[name]梨深[line]Because we're friends, right?[%p]"

msgid "21800:[name]梨深[line]「あたしにしてみれば、タクを助けてあげるのは当然なの」[%p]"
msgstr "21800:[name]梨深[line]Of course I'm going to want to help you![%p]"

msgid "21900:[name]梨深[line]「どうして、とか寂しいこと言わない！」[%p]"
msgstr "21900:[name]梨深[line]Don't ask “why.” It makes me sad![%p]"

msgid "22000:[name]梨深[line]「分かった？」[%p]"
msgstr "22000:[name]梨深[line]Got it?[%p]"

msgid "22100:[name]拓巳[line]「……う、うん」[%p]"
msgstr "22100:[name]拓巳[line]Y-Yeah.[%p]"

msgid "22200:友達として、か……。[%p]"
msgstr "22200:Friends, huh?[%p]"

msgid "22300:これが“恋人として”とかだったら僕の人生始まったなって感じだったんだけど。[%p]"
msgstr "22300:If she'd said “because you're my boyfriend,” it might've felt like a whole new life for me was about to begin.[%p]"

msgid "22400:だけど、友達としてだったとしても――[%p]"
msgstr "22400:But even if it was as friends...[%p]"

msgid "22500:すごく、嬉しい……。[%p]"
msgstr "22500:It made me so incredibly happy.[%p]"

msgid "22600:他人に優しくされること。[%p]"
msgstr "22600:Having someone else be nice to me...[%p]"

msgid "22700:他人が僕のために見返りなしでなにかをしようとしてくれること。[%p]"
msgstr "22700:Having someone do something for me without expecting a reward.[%p]"

msgid "22800:それが、こんなに嬉しいことだなんて。[%p]"
msgstr "22800:I didn't realize how happy that would make me.[%p]"

msgid "22900:もしかしたら、初めての感覚かもしれない。[%p]"
msgstr "22900:Maybe it was something I'd never experienced before.[%p]"

msgid "23000:それになにより、[%p]"
msgstr "23000:But more than that...[%p]"

msgid "23100:僕はひとりじゃないって、思わせてくれたから。[%p]"
msgstr "23100:It made me feel like I wasn't alone.[%p]"

msgid "23200:僕にとって梨深の存在は、救いだ……。[%p]"
msgstr "23200:Rimi was my salvation.[%p]"

msgid "23300:ようやく吐き気もおさまり、だいぶ気分が楽になっていた。[%p]"
msgstr "23300:The urge to throw up finally subsided, and I felt a lot better.[%p]"

msgid "23400:[name]梨深[line]「はい。使う？」[%p]"
msgstr "23400:[name]梨深[line]Here. Want this?[%p]"

msgid "23500:梨深が差し出してきたのは、フローラルな香りのする、朱色のハンカチ。[%p]"
msgstr "23500:She offered me a red handkerchief that smelled like flowers.[%p]"

msgid "23600:それを僕は素直に受け取った。[linebreak]でも、使うのがためらわれる。[%p]"
msgstr "23600:I took it. But I was hesitant to use it.[%p]"

msgid "23700:[name]梨深[line]「汚しちゃっていいよ」[%p]"
msgstr "23700:[name]梨深[line]You can get it dirty if you want.[%p]"

msgid "23800:[name]梨深[line]「タクにあげる」[%p]"
msgstr "23800:[name]梨深[line]It's yours now.[%p]"

msgid "23900:[name]拓巳[line]「あ……りがと……」[%p]"
msgstr "23900:[name]拓巳[line]T-Thank you.[%p]"

msgid "24000:申し訳ない気もしたけど、こうなったらとことん厚意は受け取っておこうって決めた。[%p]"
msgstr "24000:I felt guilty, but at this point, I decided to just take advantage of anything she'd offer me.[%p]"

msgid "24100:吐瀉物で汚れた口の端を、ハンカチで拭う。[%p]"
msgstr "24100:I wiped away the barf on the edges of my mouth.[%p]"

msgid "24200:家族以外の女の子からなにかをプレゼントしてもらったのって、初めてだ。[linebreak]これをプレゼントと呼べるかどうかは分からないけど。[%p]"
msgstr "24200:This was the first time a girl who wasn't in my family had given me a present. I wasn't sure if you could call it a present, though.[%p]"

msgid "24300:孤立無援だった僕にとって、こんな些細な物でも宝物みたいにありがたかったんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "24300:But for somebody who was totally alone, like me, even something small like this was an incredible treasure.[%p]"

msgid "24400:嬉しさとホッとした気持ちのせいで、また涙が出そうになった。[%p]"
msgstr "24400:The joy and sense of relief made me feel like I was going to cry again.[%p]"

msgid "24500:[name]梨深[line]「それじゃ、帰ろっか」[%p]"
msgstr "24500:[name]梨深[line]Now let's go home.[%p]"

msgid "24600:屈託なく、梨深が言う。[%p]"
msgstr "24600:She smiled innocently.[%p]"

msgid "24700:[name]梨深[line]「一緒に」[%p]"
msgstr "24700:[name]梨深[line]Together.[%p]"

msgid "24800:どうやらさっきの“一緒にいてあげる”っていう申し出は、すでに確定事項になったらしい。[%p]"
msgstr "24800:What she'd just said about staying with me seemed, in her mind, to be a settled matter.[%p]"

msgid "24900:僕はまだなんにも返事をしてないんだけど。[%p]"
msgstr "24900:I hadn't given an answer, but she didn't care.[%p]"

msgid "25000:もっとも、断るつもりなんてまったくなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "25000:But of course, I didn't plan on saying no.[%p]"

msgid "25100:ひとりは怖い。ひとりでいたくない。[%p]"
msgstr "25100:I was afraid of being alone. I didn't want to be alone.[%p]"

msgid "25200:今の僕には、梨深しか頼る相手がいないんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "25200:Right now, Rimi was all I could rely on.[%p]"

msgid "25300:とは言え、梨深が一緒にいてくれるからもうすべて安心、ってわけにはいかない。[%p]"
msgstr "25300:But that didn't mean that everything would be fine from now on.[%p]"

msgid "25400:帰り道はいつもと違うルートを選び、ビクビク震えながら慎重に歩を進めた。[%p]"
msgstr "25400:I still chose a different route home than usual, and I kept looking over my shoulder the whole way.[%p]"

msgid "25500:すべての物陰が危険に見えるんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "25500:Danger seemed to lurk in every shadow.[%p]"

msgid "25600:交差点に差し掛かる度に、曲がった先に優愛や『将軍』がいるかもっていう妄想に苛まれて、足がすくみ進めなくなる。[%p]"
msgstr "25600:Each time I came to an intersection, I had delusions of Yua and Shogun lurking around the corner, and froze up, unable to go forward.[%p]"

msgid "25700:すると梨深が先行し、交差する道の先を見渡してから僕に向かってうなずいて見せてくれた。[%p]"
msgstr "25700:Then Rimi would go ahead of me, looking down the street and turning back to give me a nod.[%p]"

msgid "25800:[name]梨深[line]「大丈夫、誰もいないよ」[%p]"
msgstr "25800:[name]梨深[line]Don't worry. Nobody's there.[%p]"

msgid "25900:僕はホッとして、梨深の後に付いていく。[%p]"
msgstr "25900:I gave a sigh of relief and followed her.[%p]"

msgid "26000:梨深はイヤな顔ひとつせずこんな僕に付き合ってくれた。[%p]"
msgstr "26000:Rimi stayed with me, not seeming annoyed at all.[%p]"

msgid "26100:[name]梨深[line]「ねえ、聞いていいかな？」[%p]"
msgstr "26100:[name]梨深[line]Hey, can I ask you something?[%p]"

msgid "26200:[name]梨深[line]「いったいなにがあったの？」[%p]"
msgstr "26200:[name]梨深[line]What happened?[%p]"

msgid "26300:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "26300:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "26400:梨深に話していいのかどうか、少し迷った。[%p]"
msgstr "26400:I wasn't sure whether I could tell Rimi.[%p]"

msgid "26500:ここで話すことで、梨深までが『将軍』に狙われる羽目になったら……僕が巻き込んだことになるわけで。[%p]"
msgstr "26500:If I told her and Shogun came after her, too... that would be my fault.[%p]"

msgid "26600:[name]梨深[line]「あ、話したくないなら無理に話さなくても――」[%p]"
msgstr "26600:[name]梨深[line]Oh, if you don't want to tell me, you don't have to.[%p]"

msgid "26700:[name]拓巳[line]「い、いや……」[%p]"
msgstr "26700:[name]拓巳[line]N-No...[%p]"

msgid "26800:[name]拓巳[line]「は、話す……よ……」[%p]"
msgstr "26800:[name]拓巳[line]I'll tell you.[%p]"

msgid "26900:とっさに口が動いていた。[%p]"
msgstr "26900:I started to speak.[%p]"

msgid "27000:確かに巻き込むのは気が引ける。[linebreak]でもここでなにも説明しなかったら、梨深に僕の深刻な立場を分かってもらえない。[%p]"
msgstr "27000:I was reluctant to get her involved, sure. But if I didn't explain what was going on, she wouldn't understand how desperate my situation was.[%p]"

msgid "27100:僕は僕自身のために、梨深が危険に巻き込まれる可能性についてあえて目をつむった。[%p]"
msgstr "27100:I decided to ignore the risk to her for the sake of helping myself.[%p]"

msgid "27200:彼女の方から一緒にいてくれるって言ったんだし、別にいいよね……。[%p]"
msgstr "27200:She was the one who told me she'd stay by my side... So, it was okay, right?[%p]"

msgid "27300:ニュージェネ事件の真犯人である『将軍』のこと。[%p]"
msgstr "27300:I told her about Shogun, the one behind the NewGen murders.[%p]"

msgid "27400:その手下の優愛のこと。[%p]"
msgstr "27400:About his servant, Yua.[%p]"

msgid "27500:僕はあの２人に付け狙われていること。[%p]"
msgstr "27500:That the two of them were after me.[%p]"

msgid "27600:この前の１０７前での出来事。[%p]"
msgstr "27600:What had happened in front of the 107.[%p]"

msgid "27700:それらを、何度もつっかえながら、かいつまんで説明した。[%p]"
msgstr "27700:I kept tripping over my tongue, but I managed to get it all out.[%p]"

msgid "27800:[name]梨深[line]「うーん……」[%p]"
msgstr "27800:[name]梨深[line]Hmm...[%p]"

msgid "27900:車椅子に乗った『将軍』が、僕の前に現れたときのことを話したら、梨深は渋い顔をして考え込んだ。[%p]"
msgstr "27900:When I told her about Shogun, the man in the wheelchair, she'd frowned a little.[%p]"

msgid "28000:あのときのことは梨深に一度ちゃんと聞いておきたいって思っていたことだ。これはちょうどいい機会だった。[%p]"
msgstr "28000:That was the thing I wanted to ask her about most. Now was the perfect chance to do it, too.[%p]"

msgid "28100:[name]梨深[line]「いたかなあ……車椅子のおじいさんなんて」[%p]"
msgstr "28100:[name]梨深[line]Hmm... I don't know if I remember any old men in wheelchairs.[%p]"

msgid "28200:あまり自信のなさそうな口振り。[%p]"
msgstr "28200:She didn't sound very confident.[%p]"

msgid "28300:[name]拓巳[line]「お、思い出して……っ」[%p]"
msgstr "28300:[name]拓巳[line]Remember...[%p]"

msgid "28400:[name]拓巳[line]「た、いせつな、ことだ……っ」[%p]"
msgstr "28400:[name]拓巳[line]I-It's really important.[%p]"

msgid "28500:[name]梨深[line]「でも――」[%p]"
msgstr "28500:[name]梨深[line]But...[%p]"

msgid "28600:梨深は言いにくそうに眉をひそめる。[%p]"
msgstr "28600:She paused, as if she was about to say something that was hard to say.[%p]"

msgid "28700:[name]梨深[line]「そもそもあのとき、渋谷の駅前が無人だった……なんてこと、なかったよ？」[%p]"
msgstr "28700:[name]梨深[line]The square in front of Shibuya Station wasn't empty at all, you know.[%p]"

msgid "28800:[name]梨深[line]「いつもと同じだった」[%p]"
msgstr "28800:[name]梨深[line]It was the same as ever.[%p]"

msgid "28900:あのとき、梨深にはそう見えていたんだ……。[%p]"
msgstr "28900:So she hadn't seen anything strange at all that night.[%p]"

msgid "29000:できれば、僕の言葉に同意してもらいたかったんだけど……。[%p]"
msgstr "29000:I'd hoped she'd tell me she'd seen the same things I had.[%p]"

msgid "29100:僕と梨深。どっちが見た光景が正しいのか。[%p]"
msgstr "29100:Rimi and I had seen different things. Which of us had seen what really happened?[%p]"

msgid "29200:やっぱり僕が間違ってるのかな？[linebreak]あの“無人化した渋谷”は僕の妄想だったのかな？[%p]"
msgstr "29200:Was I just wrong? Was that empty Shibuya just a delusion of mine?[%p]"

msgid "29300:でもそうなると、ちょっと問題が出てくる。[%p]"
msgstr "29300:But there was a problem, then.[%p]"

msgid "29400:無人化した渋谷に現れた、車椅子の老人――『将軍』。[%p]"
msgstr "29400:That old man in the wheelchair in the empty Shibuya... “Shogun.”[%p]"

msgid "29500:あれはどう説明すればいい？[%p]"
msgstr "29500:How could you explain him?[%p]"

msgid "29600:“無人化”が妄想だったなら、『将軍』も妄想ってことになりかねない。[%p]"
msgstr "29600:If the empty Shibuya was just a delusion, then Shogun might be a delusion, too.[%p]"

msgid "29700:[name]梨深[line]「駅前って人が多いでしょ？\u3000だから車椅子の人がいても、なかなか気が付かないだろうし」[%p]"
msgstr "29700:[name]梨深[line]There's always a lot of people in front of the station. So even if there was somebody in a wheelchair, I don't think I would've noticed.[%p]"

msgid "29800:[name]梨深[line]「要するに、見てないってこと。たはは……」[%p]"
msgstr "29800:[name]梨深[line]So, yeah... I didn't see anybody. Tahaha...[%p]"

msgid "29900:[name]梨深[line]「ごめんね。役に立てなくて……」[%p]"
msgstr "29900:[name]梨深[line]Sorry I couldn't help you.[%p]"

msgid "30000:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "30000:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "30100:少なくとも『将軍』は僕の妄想なんかじゃない。[%p]"
msgstr "30100:Shogun wasn't a delusion of mine. I was sure of that.[%p]"

msgid "30200:最初は妄想だって思ってたけど、『集団ダイブ』の映像が出てきたことでその認識は１８０度変わった。[%p]"
msgstr "30200:I'd thought he might be at first, but my opinion had changed totally after I'd seen the video of the Group Dive.[%p]"

msgid "30300:あの『将軍』は、現実だ。『将軍』は実在する。[%p]"
msgstr "30300:The Shogun who'd taken that video was real. That was proof he existed.[%p]"

msgid "30400:でも“無人化した渋谷”は妄想だった……かもしれない。[%p]"
msgstr "30400:But the empty Shibuya could've been a delusion, maybe.[%p]"

msgid "30500:あのときも駅前には人が溢れていた。[%p]"
msgstr "30500:Shibuya had been filled with people then.[%p]"

msgid "30600:僕だけがそれとは別の景色を見ていた。[%p]"
msgstr "30600:It had just looked empty to me, that was all.[%p]"

msgid "30700:それって……どういうことなんだろう……？[%p]"
msgstr "30700:But what did that mean?[%p]"

msgid "30800:[name]梨深[line]「ね、ねえ。それよりお願いがあるんだけど……いい？」[%p]"
msgstr "30800:[name]梨深[line]Hey, hey. There's something I'd like you to do with me. Is that okay?[%p]"

msgid "30900:[name]拓巳[line]「え……？」[%p]"
msgstr "30900:[name]拓巳[line]Huh?[%p]"

msgid "31000:梨深は拝むような仕草で僕に手を合わせた。[%p]"
msgstr "31000:She put her hands together, as if pleading with me.[%p]"

msgid "31100:[name]梨深[line]「ＣＤを買いに行きたいんだ。せっかくここまで来たから、ちょっと寄っていきたいんだけど」[%p]"
msgstr "31100:[name]梨深[line]I want to go buy a CD. We're really close to the shop, and I want to stop and buy it.[%p]"

msgid "31200:[name]梨深[line]「いいかな？」[%p]"
msgstr "31200:[name]梨深[line]Is that okay?[%p]"

msgid "31300:ホントは今すぐにでもベースに帰りたかった。[%p]"
msgstr "31300:To be honest, I wanted to get back to the Base as soon as possible.[%p]"

msgid "31400:こんなところまで遠回りしたのは、優愛や『将軍』が待ち伏せしている可能性を考えたからで、買い物をするためじゃない。[%p]"
msgstr "31400:I'd only taken this longer route home because I thought Shogun and Yua might be trying to set an ambush for me. I didn't want to go shopping.[%p]"

msgid "31500:ただ、ここで断ったら、僕に一緒にいてくれるって言ってくれた梨深の機嫌を損なうかもしれない。ヘタをすると、怒ってひとりで帰っちゃう恐れもある。[%p]"
msgstr "31500:But if I refused here, I might upset Rimi. She might even get mad and leave me here.[%p]"

msgid "31600:それは困る……。[linebreak]梨深には一緒にいてもらわないと……。[%p]"
msgstr "31600:That would be bad. I needed her to stay with me.[%p]"

msgid "31700:僕ひとりじゃ、ベースまで辿り着くことさえ不安だ。[%p]"
msgstr "31700:I didn't even think I could get back to the Base on my own.[%p]"

msgid "31800:結局、断れなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "31800:In the end, I wasn't able to refuse.[%p]"

msgid "31900:僕はただ梨深の後をオドオドしながらくっついていくしかない。[%p]"
msgstr "31900:I followed behind her, fear increasing with each step I took.[%p]"

msgid "32000:これだけの衆人環視の中じゃさすがの優愛も襲ってこないだろうって考えるのが普通なんだろう。[%p]"
msgstr "32000:Hopefully, even Yua would be reluctant to attack me with this many people around.[%p]"

msgid "32100:でも、この人混みに紛れてすぐ近くにヤツらが潜んでいるかもしれないっていう恐怖の方が強かった。[%p]"
msgstr "32100:But I was more scared of the idea that Shogun and Yua could be lurking in the crowds than relieved by the thought of getting lost in them.[%p]"

msgid "32200:通り過ぎる人たちと肩がぶつかりそうになるたびに、僕は心の中で悲鳴を上げていた。[%p]"
msgstr "32200:Each time somebody came close to me, I felt myself screaming internally.[%p]"

msgid "32300:[name]梨深[line]「パトカーだ……」[%p]"
msgstr "32300:[name]梨深[line]Police cars...[%p]"

msgid "32400:梨深の言葉にギクリとする。[linebreak]すぐに梨深の背中に隠れた。[%p]"
msgstr "32400:My body froze. I quickly hid behind Rimi.[%p]"

msgid "32500:確かに梨深が言う通り、パトカーが２台、道に止まっていた。[linebreak]そしてその近くに、３人の制服警官が立っている。[%p]"
msgstr "32500:She was right. There were two police cars stopped in the street. Three uniformed officers were standing next to them.[%p]"

msgid "32600:僕は警察にも追われてる。それは明らかな冤罪なんだけど、無能な警察連中はそれを分かってない。[%p]"
msgstr "32600:The police were after me, too. I hadn't actually done anything, but they were too stupid to understand that.[%p]"

msgid "32700:あの警官たちも僕のことを探してるのかな……。[%p]"
msgstr "32700:Were they looking for me, I wondered?[%p]"

msgid "32800:と思ったけど、どうやら違うみたいだった。[%p]"
msgstr "32800:But after a moment I realized they weren't.[%p]"

msgid "32900:警官たちの視線は、我が物顔で道を行進している大勢の人たちへと向けられていたんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "32900:They were staring at a crowd that was marching down the street.[%p]"

msgid "33000:デモ隊、というやつだろうか。[%p]"
msgstr "33000:A protest, maybe?[%p]"

msgid "33100:大きなメッセージボードや旗、さらにたすきや鉢巻きという定番のアイテムを身につけている。[%p]"
msgstr "33100:They were all carrying signs and waving flags, and they even had sashes and headbands.[%p]"

msgid "33200:親に手を引かれながらキョトンとした顔で行進している子供のＴシャツには、汚い字で『その目だれの目？』とマジックで書かれていて、僕は唇を噛んだ。[%p]"
msgstr "33200:There was a little girl in the rows of protestors, looking confused as she was pulled along by her parents. On her shirt, the words, “Whose eyes are those?” were written with a black magic marker. I bit my lip when I saw it.[%p]"

msgid "33300:[name]梨深[line]「なんのデモだろうね」[%p]"
msgstr "33300:[name]梨深[line]What are they protesting?[%p]"

msgid "33400:行進している人たちは、老若男女関係なくさまざまだ。[%p]"
msgstr "33400:The crowd was full of men and women, and the people were of all ages.[%p]"

msgid "33500:粛々と行進しているけど、たまにシュプレヒコールも上がっている。[%p]"
msgstr "33500:As they marched, they'd sometimes yell out slogans.[%p]"

msgid "33600:[name]デモ隊[line]「悪魔を渋谷から追い出せー！」[%p]"
msgstr "33600:[name]デモ隊[line]“Drive the demons out of Shibuya!”[%p]"

msgid "33700:[name]梨深[line]「悪魔……？」[%p]"
msgstr "33700:[name]梨深[line]Demons?[%p]"

msgid "33800:メッセージボードに書かれている内容は『悪魔を街から追い出せ！』[linebreak]『渋谷をテロリストから守れ！』というようなものが多い。[%p]"
msgstr "33800:Some of the signs said things like, “Drive the demons out of Shibuya!” Or, “Protect Shibuya from terrorists!”[%p]"

msgid "33900:きっと、ニュージェネ事件への抗議みたいなものだろう。[%p]"
msgstr "33900:It was probably a protest over the NewGen murders.[%p]"

msgid "34000:デモをしたって意味ないよ……。[%p]"
msgstr "34000:Protesting wasn't going to accomplish anything.[%p]"

msgid "34100:そんなことをしている暇があるなら、『将軍』を見つけて殺してよ。[linebreak]そうしたら僕ももう不安にならなくて済むから……。[%p]"
msgstr "34100:If they had time to protest, they should just find and kill Shogun instead. Then I wouldn't have to feel so scared all the time.[%p]"

msgid "34200:[name]梨深[line]「タク、行こっ」[%p]"
msgstr "34200:[name]梨深[line]Taku, let's go.[%p]"

msgid "34300:梨深は興味なさげにデモ隊から視線をそむけると、ＣＤショップの入り口に向かってさっさと歩き始めた。[%p]"
msgstr "34300:Rimi looked away from the protestors, seemingly disinterested, and began to walk toward the CD shop.[%p]"

msgid "34400:店内に入って梨深がまっすぐ向かったのは、インディーズＣＤのコーナーだった。[%p]"
msgstr "34400:Once inside, she headed straight for the indie CD corner.[%p]"

msgid "34500:Ｊ－ＰＯＰのコーナーと違って、この辺は客があまりいない。[%p]"
msgstr "34500:Unlike the J-Pop section, there weren't many people here.[%p]"

msgid "34600:梨深は“Ｐ”の棚のところで立ち止まり、目当てのＣＤを探し始める。[%p]"
msgstr "34600:She stopped in front of the “P” shelf and began to look for a CD.[%p]"

msgid "34700:でもすぐに、シュンとして肩を落とした。[%p]"
msgstr "34700:But she quickly gave up.[%p]"

msgid "34800:[name]梨深[line]「うーん、やっぱりないなあ……」[%p]"
msgstr "34800:[name]梨深[line]Hmm... it's not here.[%p]"

msgid "34900:インディーズで、頭文字がＰのアーティストって、もしかして……[%p]"
msgstr "34900:An indie band whose name started with P. Could it be...[%p]"

msgid "35000:[name]梨深[line]「タクは、ファンタズムってバンド知ってる？\u3000今、話題になってるけど」[%p]"
msgstr "35000:[name]梨深[line]Taku, have you heard of Phantasm? They're really big right now.[%p]"

msgid "35100:やっぱりか……。[linebreak]知らないはずがない。ライブまで見に行ったし、ＣＤも持ってる。[%p]"
msgstr "35100:I should've guessed that was what she was after. Of course I knew about them. I'd gone to a concert, and even owned a CD.[%p]"

msgid "35200:僕がうなずくと、梨深は苦笑した。[%p]"
msgstr "35200:I nodded, and she chuckled.[%p]"

msgid "35300:[name]梨深[line]「あたし、そういう情報はけっこう疎くて、最近になって知ったんだぁ」[%p]"
msgstr "35300:[name]梨深[line]I don't really know a lot about that stuff. I only found out about them recently.[%p]"

msgid "35400:[name]梨深[line]「それで友達に借りようかと思ったんだけど、なかなか手に入らないらしくて誰も持ってないんだよ」[%p]"
msgstr "35400:[name]梨深[line]I thought about borrowing their CD from a friend, but it's hard to get. Nobody has it.[%p]"

msgid "35500:[name]梨深[line]「だからＣＤ買うしかないかなーって思ってここ一週間ぐらいあちこち探してみたんだけど、どこも売り切れ中」[%p]"
msgstr "35500:[name]梨深[line]So, I thought maybe a CD shop would have it. I've been looking for about a week, but it's out of stock everywhere.[%p]"

msgid "35600:[name]梨深[line]「次はいつ入るんだろ……」[%p]"
msgstr "35600:[name]梨深[line]When do you think they'll get more in?[%p]"

msgid "35700:[name]拓巳[line]「ぼ……僕……」[%p]"
msgstr "35700:[name]拓巳[line]I-I...[%p]"

msgid "35800:[name]拓巳[line]「持って……る……」[%p]"
msgstr "35800:[name]拓巳[line]I've got it.[%p]"

msgid "35900:と、梨深は目を丸くした。[%p]"
msgstr "35900:Rimi's eyes went wide.[%p]"

msgid "36000:[name]梨深[line]「持ってるって……ＣＤ？」[%p]"
msgstr "36000:[name]梨深[line]You... have the CD?[%p]"

msgid "36100:うなずいて見せる。[linebreak]すると梨深は――[%p]"
msgstr "36100:I nodded. And then Rimi...[%p]"

msgid "36200:僕の肩に手を置いてきた。[%p]"
msgstr "36200:put her hands on my shoulders.[%p]"

msgid "36300:いきなり顔を近づけられて、僕はドギマギしてしまう。[%p]"
msgstr "36300:Her face was so close, I almost flinched.[%p]"

msgid "36400:梨深の髪から漂うシャンプーのいい香りが僕の鼻をくすぐって、自分の顔がカーッと熱くなるのが分かった。[%p]"
msgstr "36400:The smell of her shampoo tickled my nostrils, and I could feel my face turning red.[%p]"

msgid "36500:[name]梨深[line]「ねえタク……取引しよう」[%p]"
msgstr "36500:[name]梨深[line]Hey, Taku. Let's make a trade.[%p]"

msgid "36600:と、取引……？[%p]"
msgstr "36600:T-Trade...[%p]"

msgid "36700:[name]梨深[line]「そのＣＤ貸してくれたら、見返りにあたし……」[%p]"
msgstr "36700:[name]梨深[line]If you give me that CD, in exchange, I'll...[%p]"

msgid "36800:やけに深刻な表情で見つめてくる。[%p]"
msgstr "36800:Her face was dead serious.[%p]"

msgid "36900:僕はゴクリと息を呑んだ。[linebreak]見返りって……なんだろう。[%p]"
msgstr "36900:I gulped. I'll what?[%p]"

